    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <div class="scard p-8">
        <div style="width:52px;height:52px;border-radius:14px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;background:rgba(230,168,23,.1);margin-bottom:1rem">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#E6A817" stroke-width="2"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:1.35rem;color:#1A1A1A;margin-bottom:.75rem">Shingle Wind Damage</h3>
        <p style="color:#555555;font-size:.95rem;line-height:1.7">St. Pete's coastal winds frequently lift, crack, or tear off shingles. We match your existing shingle color and style and replace damaged sections to restore full weather protection.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="scard p-8">
        <div style="width:52px;height:52px;border-radius:14px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;background:rgba(230,168,23,.1);margin-bottom:1rem">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#E6A817" stroke-width="2"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:1.35rem;color:#1A1A1A;margin-bottom:.75rem">Tile Repair & Replacement</h3>
        <p style="color:#555555;font-size:.95rem;line-height:1.7">The barrel and flat tiles on St. Petersburg's many Spanish-style homes crack over time from thermal expansion and debris impact. We source matching tiles and reseat them to prevent leaks.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="scard p-8">
        <div style="width:52px;height:52px;border-radius:14px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;background:rgba(230,168,23,.1);margin-bottom:1rem">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#E6A817" stroke-width="2"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:1.35rem;color:#1A1A1A;margin-bottom:.75rem">Flashing & Sealant Failures</h3>
        <p style="color:#555555;font-size:.95rem;line-height:1.7">The most common source of roof leaks in St. Pete. We replace deteriorated flashing at chimneys, walls, valleys, and pipe boots with durable materials that resist salt air corrosion.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- OUR PROCESS -->
<section class="py-20" style="background:#FFFFFF">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-5">
    <div class="text-center mb-14">
      <p class="sl gt mb-3">How It Works</p>
      <h2 style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:clamp(2rem,4vw,3rem);line-height:.95;color:#1A1A1A;letter-spacing:-.01em">OUR REPAIR PROCESS</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
      <div class="scard p-8 flex gap-5">
        <div class="step-num">1</div>
        <div>
          <h3 style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:1.2rem;color:#1A1A1A;margin-bottom:.5rem">Damage Assessment</h3>
          <p style="color:#555555;font-size:.95rem;line-height:1.7">Thorough inspection with photo documentation to identify all damage - not just the obvious spots. You get an honest explanation of what needs repair.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="scard p-8 flex gap-5">
        <div class="step-num">2</div>
        <div>
          <h3 style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:1.2rem;color:#1A1A1A;margin-bottom:.5rem">Transparent Quote</h3>
          <p style="color:#555555;font-size:.95rem;line-height:1.7">Written estimate with itemized costs. No hidden fees, no pressure to replace when a repair will do the job.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="scard p-8 flex gap-5">
        <div class="step-num">3</div>
        <div>
          <h3 style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:1.2rem;color:#1A1A1A;margin-bottom:.5rem">Professional Repair</h3>
          <p style="color:#555555;font-size:.95rem;line-height:1.7">Quality materials matched to your existing roof, expert installation, and complete property protection throughout the process.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="scard p-8 flex gap-5">
        <div class="step-num">4</div>
        <div>
          <h3 style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:1.2rem;color:#1A1A1A;margin-bottom:.5rem">Follow-Up & Warranty</h3>
          <p style="color:#555555;font-size:.95rem;line-height:1.7">We follow up to confirm the repair is holding and you are satisfied. All work is backed by our workmanship warranty.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- SERVICE AREA -->
<section class="py-20" style="background:#F7F7F7">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-5">
    <div class="text-center mb-10">
      <p class="sl gt mb-3">St. Petersburg Service Area</p>
      <h2 style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:clamp(2rem,4vw,3rem);line-height:.95;color:#1A1A1A;letter-spacing:-.01em;margin-bottom:1rem">ST. PETERSBURG NEIGHBORHOODS WE SERVE</h2>
      <p style="color:#555555;font-size:1rem;line-height:1.75;max-width:700px;margin:0 auto">Happy Roof provides roof repair throughout St. Petersburg and Pinellas County.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-3 md:grid-cols-4 lg:grid-cols-5 gap-3 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
